From: Xinyu Chen <xinyu.chen@freescale.com>
Date: Fri, 29 Aug 2008 11:18:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ENGR00089618 Increase DMA zone size for MX51

Make DMA zone size to 32MB in default config

Signed-off-by: Xinyu Chen <xinyu.chen@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx51_3stack_defconfig |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx51_3stack_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx51_3stack_defconfig
index b0127cd..c5cef7a 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx51_3stack_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx51_3stack_defconfig
@@ -182,7 +182,7 @@ CONFIG_ARCH_MXC_HAS_NFC_V3_2=y
 # Device options
 #
 CONFIG_MXC_TZIC=y
-CONFIG_DMA_ZONE_SIZE=24
+CONFIG_DMA_ZONE_SIZE=32
 CONFIG_UTMI_MXC=y
 
 #
